---
// src/components/TrustSection.astro
---

<div
    class="bg-card rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 shadow-lg shadow-black/2 dark:shadow-none max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16 p-8"
>
    <section class="text-center w-full m-0 p-0">
        <p class="text-secondary text-sm mb-2">
            I'm building this with feedback from home baristas on
            <a
                href="https://www.reddit.com/r/latteart/comments/1jqfwqd/comment/ml7yh05/?utm_source=share&utm_medium=web3x&utm_name=web3xcss&utm_term=1&utm_content=share_button"
                target="_blank"
                class="bg-accent text-on-accent px-1.5 py-0.5 mx-0.5 rounded-full no-underline font-medium inline-block leading-tight transition-opacity duration-200 hover:opacity-80"
                rel="noopener noreferrer">Reddit</a
            >
            – here's what they're saying:
        </p>
        <blockquote
            class="mt-4 mb-3 mx-auto pl-6 italic text-lg text-primary border-l-4 border-indigo-300 dark:border-indigo-500 text-left inline-block max-w-[90%]"
        >
            "This is a BRILLIANT idea and I WILL be downloading this as soon as
            it's released"
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary mt-2">– Reddit user</p>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote
            class="mt-6 mb-3 mx-auto pl-6 italic text-lg text-primary border-l-4 border-indigo-300 dark:border-indigo-500 text-left inline-block max-w-[90%]"
        >
            "I have a photo album in chronological order and I’m relying on
            muscle memory and handwritten notes to up my game."
            <p class="text-sm text-secondary mt-2">– Another Reddit user</p>
        </blockquote>
    </section>
</div>
